                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1840</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Make sure that for all languages all generated files are removed when running a build.sh clean.&lt;br/&gt;
